title: NFL Week 10 Fantasy Advice + Early Gambling Leans (Football 11/08)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Heath Cummings to break down Week 10 from a fantasy angle and to debate whether or not Dez Bryant is a good fantasy add. Then Kelly Stewart joins Will to talk about the books getting hammered last week, what it could mean for Week 10 and what her SuperContest picks are after plugging them in at the Westgate on Wednesday.
